MBOMBELA &#8211; Police are investigating an assault case in which four men allegedly beat up a 19-year-old golfer at Nelspruit Golf Club (NGC) last Saturday.According to SAPS spokesman, Sgt Gerald Sedibe, the case has been sent to the senior public prosecutor for a decision. No charges have been laid and no arrests have been made as yet.Mr Jabulane Mabilane said he was practising on the seventh green when a four-ball, playing the sixth hole, said he was not allowed to do so. &#8220;They then asked if I was a member at the club. I said I was and continued to play the eighth hole.